<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="CH2b1633-de-aff65a3b" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Translation of 王羲之集二卷 into (German)</title><editor role="translator">HeidelbergSoSe24</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="1"><ab>This work is in the public domain</ab></availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>Translation of 王羲之集二卷 into (German)</title></bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#CH2b1633"><title xml:lang="och">王羲之集二卷</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="de">German</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#dsehnal">Initially created: <date>2024-06-13T21:49:44.988+09:00</date> by dsehnal</creation><creation resp="#dsehnal">Header modified: <date>2024-06-15T03:40:51.478+09:00</date> by dsehnal</creation><creation resp="#dsehnal">Header modified: <date>2024-06-15T03:41:33.532+09:00</date> by dsehnal</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="CH2b1633-start"><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T03:43:48.837+09:00">Vorrede zu der Orchideen-Pavillon Sammlung </seg><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T04:22:37.437+09:00">Im neunten Jahr der Yonghe-Era</seg><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T03:46:11.761+09:00">befand sich der Jupiter-Planet in der Guichou-Position.</seg><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T03:46:53.123+09:00">Am Anfang des späten Frühjahrs</seg><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T04:10:33.279+09:00">sammelten wir uns bei dem Orchideen-Pavillon im Shanyin-Bezirk des Kuaiji-Kreises,</seg><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T04:10:59.254+09:00">weil die Fest der Beseitigung des Übles statt fand. </seg><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T03:53:48.45+09:00">Die allen Würdigen sind komplett angekommen,</seg><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T04:11:24.263+09:00">die Jungen und Alten haben sich völlig gesammelt.</seg><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T05:35:01.499+09:00">Hier gab es erhabene Berge und hohe Bergketten,</seg><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T05:14:11.955+09:00">üppige Wälder und schön gewachsener Bambus.</seg><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T04:12:04.022+09:00">Außerdem gab es da einen klaren Wasserstrom, der rasch floss, </seg><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T04:15:42.923+09:00">und der die Streifen [der Naturszenerien] von beiden Seiten reflektierte. </seg><seg corresp="#CH2b1633_CHANT_002-383a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-06-15T04:19:40.99+09:00">Es lockte uns dazu, ihn in den Meander, auf dem man die Weinbecher schwimmen läßt, umzuwandeln,</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>